                        <div type="writingAct"><opener>
                                        <dateline sameAs="MBDatumszeile">
                                                <hi rend="smallcaps"><hi rendition="#mPrint">Industrial Newspaper
                                                  Company,<lb/>(limited.)</hi></hi></dateline>
                                        <salute sameAs="MBAnrede"><hi rend="italic smallcaps"><hi rendition="#i"><hi rendition="#mPrint">Sir,</hi></hi></hi></salute>
                                </opener><p rend="MBTextMitEinzug"><hi rendition="#i"><hi rendition="#mPrint">You are urgently requested to
                                                  attend </hi></hi><seg type="comment"><orig><hi rendition="#i"><hi rendition="#mPrint">a Meeting
                                                  of Shareholders on the 19th day of </hi></hi>
                                                  March <hi rendition="#mPrint">1866,</hi></orig><note xml:id="b02b7f37-e0de-483a-bc65-17bddb75de6c">Die
                                                  Sitzung der Aktionäre der <orgName key="ed_isw_cry_sy">Industrial Newspaper Company
                                                  (Limited)</orgName> (<ref target="B00007/#nmrb_qzn_4y">Erl. zu Marx an J.
                                                  Ph. Becker, zwischen 9. und
                                                  15.1.1866</ref><?oxy_comment_start author="lindenberg" timestamp="20170517T110013+0200" comment="{{Erl. 6f}}"?>)<?oxy_comment_end?>
                                                  fand am 19.&#160;März 1866 statt. Siehe <ref target="B00075/#start_odz_25z_nz">Marx an Engels,
                                                  24.3.1866</ref>
                                                  <?oxy_comment_start author="reichhoff" timestamp="20170412T170418+0200" comment="{{Br. 72.35–36}}"?>.<?oxy_comment_end?></note></seg>
                                        <hi rendition="#i"><hi rendition="#mPrint">at the Company’s
                                                  Offices, <hi rendition="#u">1</hi><hi rendition="#u">8, Bouverie-street,
                                                  Fleet-street,</hi> for the purpose of considering
                                                  the propriety of increasing the nominal capital of
                                                  the Company.</hi></hi></p><closer sameAs="MBUnterschrift"><hi rendition="#mPrint">R.&#160;Applegarth, </hi><lb/><hi rend="italic smallcaps"><hi rendition="#i"><hi rendition="#mPrint">Secretary</hi>.</hi></hi><dateline><hi rend="italic smallcaps"><hi rendition="#i"><hi rendition="#mPrint">18, Bouverie
                                                  Street.—January</hi></hi></hi><hi rend="italic smallcaps" xml:space="preserve"> 31</hi><hi rend="italic smallcaps"><hi rendition="#i"><hi rendition="#mPrint"><hi rendition="#mPrint">st,</hi></hi></hi></hi>
                                                <hi rend="smallcaps">1866.</hi></dateline></closer><lb/><pb/> My Dear Sir<p sameAs="MBTextohneEinzug">I beg you will favour us with your
                                        presence on <seg type="comment"><orig>Monday
                                                  <?oxy_comment_start author="lindenberg" timestamp="20170503T160045+0200" comment="alternative Lesung: Eight"?><unclear reason="illegible" cert="high">hften</unclear><?oxy_comment_end?> at the
                                                  Directors Meeting.</orig><note xml:id="ecbd623b-323f-412c-b252-a3447d9ff39b">Die
                                                  Sitzung des Direktoriums fand Montag, den
                                                  12.&#160;März 1866 statt. Siehe <ref target="B00075/#start_l5m_hvz_nz">Marx an Engels,
                                                  24.3.<?oxy_comment_start author="reichhoff" timestamp="20170412T171241+0200" comment="Br. 72.25–38"?>1866<?oxy_comment_end?></ref>.</note></seg></p><p sameAs="MBTextmitEinzug">I have also the pleasure to inform
                                        you that at the shareholders Meeting yourself with <seg type="comment"><orig>4&#160;others</orig><note xml:id="dcdfcba0-7be6-420c-9c96-bd8005376d6c"><persName key="pdrPo.001.004.000001603">Peter
                                                  Fox</persName>, <persName key="pdrPo.001.004.000002244">George
                                                  Howell</persName>, <persName key="pdrPo.001.004.000005083">John
                                                  Weston</persName> und <persName key="ed_z5s_ptj_wx">Arthur Miall</persName>. Siehe
                                                  <ref target="B00036/#start_kvh_s5z_nz">Marx an
                                                  Engels,
                                                  10.2.<?oxy_comment_start author="reichhoff" timestamp="20170412T170841+0200" comment="{{Br. 33.41–43}}"?>1866<?oxy_comment_end?></ref>.</note></seg>
                                        was appointed <seg type="comment"><orig>a Comittee to
                                                  supervise the matter</orig><note xml:id="nfgm_2mt_zy">Siehe <ref target="B00036/#start_kvh_s5z_nz">Marx an Engels,
                                                  10.2.<?oxy_comment_start author="reichhoff" timestamp="20170412T172041+0200" comment="{{Br. 33.39–44}"?>1866<?oxy_comment_end?></ref></note></seg>
                                        to go into <seg type="comment"><orig>the Paper.</orig><note xml:id="nswf_4pt_zy">„The Commonwealth” (London).
                                                  (((zThe_Commonwealth)))</note></seg></p><closer sameAs="MBUnterschrift"><!--<hi rend="color(0000FF)">{u2}</hi>-->I am <expan resp="editor" sameAs="dottet_underline">D<ex>ea</ex>r</expan> Sir<lb/>yours
                                                truly<lb/>RApplegarth<lb/><expan resp="editor" sameAs="dottet_underline">Sec<ex>retary</ex></expan></closer><p rend="MBTextOhneEinzug">Dr Marx </p></div>
                </body>
